text: Victoria Chaplina (born 23 October 1988 Sverdlovsk) is a Russian volleyball player. She played for the Women's National Team at the 2013 FIVB Women's World Grand Champions Cup. and the 2013 Summer Universiade, She played for Dynamo Kazan. == References == == External links == * * * http://www.russiavolley.com/4233/victoria-chaplina-moves-from-uralochka-to- dinamo-kazan/ * Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Russian women's volleyball players Category:Universiade gold medalists for Russia Category:Universiade medalists in volleyball
